'''Andy King''' (23 July 1942<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.worldfootball.net/player_summary/andy-king_3/|title=Andy King|website=worldfootball.net}}</ref> – 23 February 2015)<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11791/9730143/kilmarnock-have-announced-former-defender-andy-king-has-died|title=Kilmarnock have announced former defender Andy King has died|publisher=skysports.com|date=24 February 2015}}</ref> was a Scottish professional [[association football|footballer]] who played for [[Kilmarnock F.C.|Kilmarnock]], as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neilbrown.newcastlefans.com/kilmarnock/kilmarnock.html|title=KILMARNOCK : 1946/47 - 2012/13|accessdate=26 April 2014|publisher=Post War English & Scottish Football League A - Z Player's Transfer Database}}</ref>

